rules:
## LinkedIn: stay on .com (DNS/hosts still in overwrite.sh)
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,linkedin.com,全球代理
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,licdn.com,全球代理
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,linkedin.cn,REJECT
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,licdn.cn,REJECT
## Apple TV+ / Music / News only (same idea as Netflix/Disney+); rest of Apple stays DIRECT
- RULE-SET,AppleMedia,手动选择
## Mail SMTP + Rebrickable (managed)
## Firstrade DIRECT + smtp.gmail.com -> gmail-out injected in overwrite.sh
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mail.me.com,DIRECT
- DOMAIN-KEYWORD,smtp.mail,DIRECT
- DOMAIN,smtp.googlemail.com,DIRECT
- DOMAIN,smtp-relay.gmail.com,DIRECT
- DOMAIN,smtp.purelymail.com,DIRECT
- DOMAIN,smtp.mail.me.com,DIRECT
- DOMAIN-SUFFIX,rebrickable.com,🇪🇸 西班牙 01
- DOMAIN,rebrickable.com,🇪🇸 西班牙 01
- DOMAIN,www.rebrickable.com,🇪🇸 西班牙 01
